2015-06-01 22:16:19 +0300 Phil Carmody <phil@dovecot.fi> (6aadd1c)

    various: use new uni_utf8_get_char*() interface No need for additional
    uni_utf8_char_bytes() calls if you can parse and know the size with one
    call.

