2012-10-03 18:17:26 +0300 Timo Sirainen <tss@iki.fi> (bdd36cf)

    Renamed network.[ch] to net.[ch]. The function prefixes already started with
    net_ instead of network_. And icecap wants to use network.h for other
    purpose. :)


